    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it polished and pristine inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find one cleaner than this! Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it! \ud83d\ude0a",
